Extract a message template from source code:

  xgettext -j -o locale/messages.pot gnakb.py

Genrate a localized message file:

  msginit --locale=de --input=locale/messages.pot --output=locale/de/LC_MESSAGES/gnakb.po

Compile localized messages:

  msgfmt -o locale/de/LC_MESSAGES/gnakb.mo locale/de/LC_MESSAGES/gnakb.po

